title: Mythology - Folklore of the Menomini Indians (pdf) EarthBow
description:
Skinner, Alanson - Folklore of the Menomini Indians, 1915, 338 pages

originally published in the Anthropological Papers of the American Museum of Natural History, and is a nice collection of myths, legends, and folklore from this Wisconsin tribe.


Note: I will be adding many more titles soon, Search for "EarthBow" for a list of available titles.

As always, comments (good or bad) are appreciated
